================================================================================

Project: Intelligent Recommender System
Author: Geoffrey Wang
GitHub: https://github.com/GeoffreyWang1117/Intelligent-Recommender
Description: A dual-teacher recommendation system combining traditional machine 
             learning algorithms with large language models for intelligent 
             movie recommendations.

Key Features:
- Traditional Teachers: 6 state-of-the-art recommendation algorithms
- LLM Teachers: Llama3 (English) + Qwen3 (Chinese) dual-language support
- Comprehensive evaluation framework with 4-category metrics
- Production-ready Docker deployment
- Complete documentation and phase summaries

Academic and Research Use:
This project is particularly suited for:
- Educational purposes in recommendation system courses
- Research on hybrid recommendation architectures
- Comparative studies between traditional and LLM-based approaches
- Open-source contribution to the recommendation system community

For commercial use, please contact the author for licensing arrangements.
